SELECT [q].[Question], [q].[Distributor], [q].[PartyHllcode], [q].[PartyMasterCode], CASE
    WHEN [t].[Id] IS NOT NULL AND [t].[Answer] IS NOT NULL THEN [t].[Answer]
    ELSE N''
END, CASE
    WHEN [t].[Id] IS NOT NULL AND [t].[PhotoData] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [t].[PhotoData]
FROM [QuestionsNew] AS [q]
LEFT JOIN [Tbl_ReviewAnswers] AS [t] ON [q].[Distributor] = [t].[Rscode]
WHERE CONVERT(date, [t].[CreatedAt]) >= @__startDate_0 AND CONVERT(date, [t].[CreatedAt]) <= @__endDate_1 AND [t].[Rscode] = @__rscode_2 AND [t].[EmpNo] = @__UserId_3 AND [t].[QuestionId] = [q].[QuestionId] AND [t].[Outlet] = [q].[PartyHllcode]
ORDER BY [t].[CreatedAt] DESC

Executing controller action with signature System.Threading.Tasks.Task`1[Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc.IActionResult] FilteredReviewAnswers(System.String, System.String, System.Nullable`1[System.DateTime], System.Nullable`1[System.DateTime]) on controller MR_Application_New.Controllers.ReviewPlaneController (MR_Application_New).
2025-01-30 18:13:21.816 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (8ms) [Parameters=[@__startDate_0='?' (DbType = DateTime), @__endDate_1='?' (DbType = DateTime), @__rscode_2='?' (Size = 255), @__UserId_3='?' (Size = 255)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [q].[Question], [q].[Distributor], [q].[PartyHllcode], [q].[PartyMasterCode], CASE
    WHEN [t].[Id] IS NOT NULL AND [t].[Answer] IS NOT NULL THEN [t].[Answer]
    ELSE N''
END, CASE
    WHEN [t].[Id] IS NOT NULL AND [t].[PhotoData] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [t].[PhotoData]
FROM [QuestionsNew] AS [q]
LEFT JOIN [Tbl_ReviewAnswers] AS [t] ON [q].[Distributor] = [t].[Rscode]
WHERE CONVERT(date, [t].[CreatedAt]) >= @__startDate_0 AND CONVERT(date, [t].[CreatedAt]) <= @__endDate_1 AND [t].[Rscode] = @__rscode_2 AND [t].[EmpNo] = @__UserId_3 AND [t].[QuestionId] = [q].[QuestionId] AND [t].[Outlet] = [q].[PartyHllcode]
ORDER BY [t].[CreatedAt] DESC

SELECT [q].[QuestionId], [q].[Ba], [q].[CreatedAt], [q].[DeletedAt], [q].[Distributor], [q].[PartyHllcode], [q].[PartyMasterCode], [q].[PartyName], [q].[Question], [q].[Status], [q].[Type], [q].[UpdatedAt], [q0].[OptionId], [q0].[OptionText], [q0].[QuestionId]
FROM [QuestionsNew] AS [q]
